headline.print_headline: Donaldson Wins Czech Masters, Makes Ryder Cup
headline.main: Donaldson Wins Czech Masters, Makes Ryder Cup

lead_paragraph: Jamie Donaldson shot 4-under 68 Sunday to win the Czech Masters and secure a spot on the European Ryder Cup team.
